'''Ioulaum''' was a great archwizard of [[Netheril]], a beloved champion of his people and the inventor of both the [[mythallar]] and the flying enclaves of his empire. When Ioulaum abandoned Netheril to escape the ''life drain'' dweomers of the [[phaerimm]] in {{Yearlink|-339}}, panic spread at the news of his disappearance, leading to [[Karsus]] casting his spell ''[[Karsus's avatar]]''. After the fall of Netheril, Ioulaum survived as an [[elder brain]] [[lich]].
